      <title>乌克兰议员希望在基辅广场树立罗纳德·里根雕像</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/09/nx-s1-5031295/ukrainian-parliamentarian-wants-a-statue-of-ronald-reagan-in-kiev-square</link>
